": null, "text": "Re Bob: pad用起来还行，电脑目前是笔记本，准备换台式（这个势在必行）", "timestamp": 1626772966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2102613, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 408739, "reply_to": 2102440, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是这个mba吧，确实是电脑不假，但是拓展性比ipad感觉也就半斤八两，反正都是离不开拓展坞。而且这样我上课就要带笔记本和ipad两样，更麻烦一些。\nmacbook选项优点显然就是macOS电脑系统，但是我的专业软件都在windows上，我用macOS也就只能做做文档什么的。我也没用过macOS", "timestamp": 1626773421, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2107878, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 408739, "reply_to": 2102613, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我自己感觉你选便宜的就好，做做文档pad和mba都行", "timestamp": 1626848975, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 408739, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "macbookair m1 v.s. ipad pro 12.9 m1\n选哪个？", "timestamp": 1626770463, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626848977, "url": "", "vote": {}}}